[1] New Design\nBrother iPrint&Scan has a fresh new design for a better experience. Before using this app please select your device from the top menu.
[2] New Editing Tools\nThree new editing tools have been added (Scale, Straighten & Crop).
[3] Fax Send*\nYou can send a fax from your mobile device.
[4] Fax Preview*\nYou can view received faxes stored on your machine from your mobile device.
[5] Copy Preview*\nPreview an image and edit it before copying.
[6] Machine Status*\nYou can view the machine’s status such as ink/toner volume and error messages from your mobile device.
[7] Note\n“*” only available on new models. Please tap “i” (top right) for a list of supported models.
